law.text: The license fees for professional engineers and professional land surveyors shall be established by administrative regulation promulgated by the board. If the board refuses to issue a license to any applicant, the initial fee deposited shall be retained as an application fee.
law.history: Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 214, sec. 11, effective January 1, 1999. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 291, sec. 9, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 313, sec. 8, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 148, sec. 7. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1599e-13.
